<tr><td colspan="2"> </td><td class='diff-marker'>+</td><td class='diff-addedline'><div><ins class="diffchange">=== {{incharacter|My left leg just turned blue after zombie bit me and my player info says I have a bite wound! Is it bad?}} ===</ins></div></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2"> </td><td class='diff-marker'>+</td><td class='diff-addedline'><div><ins class="diffchange">Yes, very. You should disinfect the bite wound ASAP with [[Disinfectant|disinfectant]] or something similar, or if it's not available - cauterize the wound with something hot(a [[Hotplate|hotplate]] or a knife and a [[Lighter|lighter]] will suffice). If you don't treat the wound in six hours or so, it will turn into [[Infection|infection]], which is much worse and liable to kill you, unless you take [[Antibiotic|antibiotics]].</ins></div></td></tr>
